high_descs: Turn left, turn left at the window to face the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Pick up the egg in front of the coffee maker on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the stove on the right, look up above the stove at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the egg inside the microwave, heat the egg, open the microwave door, take the egg out of the microwave.
Turn left, turn left at the end of the island and face the black bin on the floor.
Put the egg inside of the black bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: To heat an egg and place it inside the black bin.

high_descs: Turn left move forward then face the counter with coffee maker
Pick up the egg in front of the coffee maker
Turn left then head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in and out the egg then close the microwave
Turn left then walk forward head to the trash bin on your left
Drop the egg in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Dispose the heated egg in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn left, move to the window, turn left, go to the egg on the counter.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Bring the egg to the left, to the microwave over the stove.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Bring the heated egg to the left, around the side of the island, to the trash can next to the island.
Put the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the trash can.
